data.title: Offers 2012 S MH
data.meta_description: Offers 2012 s Mh - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. The document is a guide to university offers published by the Herald newspaper in conjunction with the Universities Admissions Centre (UAC). It provides information on the main round of university offers that occurred in October through December and early January, including a list of course cut-offs and a full list of students receiving offers. It also discusses two students, Henrietta Longmuir and Catherine Gamble, who are awaiting their university offer results and have various options and backup plans depending on whether they receive their preferred offers.
